Quickstrike:









"Uh, ya got uh CR chamber?" Quickstrike asked, his voice a little wobbily. 
"Ah needs to do that before we go anywhere. Ah really don't cares 'bout 
Megatron. Hell Beast's th' one ah wanna whoop!" He snapped his pincher in 
anger.

"Ah even reformated his ship t' th' Darkside's files. Ah's the only one that 
can fix 'er. He can't even get commandes t' 'er. She won't take commands 
from anyones, but me. She won't take any programing." He chuckled to 
himself. Then he realized something. He pointed his working claw to him. "If 
ya tell any of his kiester kissers that, ah'll tear out yer mother board, ya 
hear?" He thought that he shouldn't have told him that. It could mean his 
life. He had told only Megatron about this.
